title: Saracens ARFC Sonics Charity Shield raffle
summary: Here's your chance to win BIG, in the Saracens ARFC Sonics Charity Shield raffle! This autumn our burgeoning junior girls' rugby section, the Saracens ARFC Sonics, are raising money for Wooden Spoon, the children's charity of rugby. To that end, they've not only launched a new tournament in the junior girls' rugby calendar - the Charity Shield - they're giving you the chance to win one or more of several fantastic prizes, including an entire junior rugby team's worth of tickets to see the Red Roses face Ireland in the Women's Six Nations. So, don't miss your chance to win BIG! And know that, by simply taking part, you'll be helping raise vital funds for Wooden Spoon and the disadvantaged children they support. Thank you in advance from all at Saracens ARFC Sonics!
